                    "@type": "Question",
                    "name": "Does Bertrand Brands work with Sudbury businesses?",
                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "Yes. Bertrand Brands is based in Greater Sudbury, Ontario and works with local businesses across Sudbury and Northern Ontario, as well as clients across Canada."
                    }
                },
                {
                    "@type": "Question",
                    "name": "How much does a website cost for a small business in Sudbury?",
                    "acceptedAnswer": {
                        "@type": "Answer",
                        "text": "Bertrand Brands offers fixed-price website packages starting at $750 CAD for a Starter Site (delivered in 1 business day) and $1,250 CAD for a fully custom One-Page Redesign (2\u20133 business days). No hourly billing."
